Start the app with command: npm start

Post request to SignIn with the hardcoded User to get token
Send body with Json request
{
  "username": "Test",
  "password": "TestPass"
}
http://localhost:4000/api/signin


Get request for getting all products:
http://localhost:4000/api/products

Post request for creating a product:
Set the headers in format Authorization: Bearer token
{
  "name": "Computer",
  "category": "Hardware",
  "price": 2500
}
http://localhost:4000/api/products

Put request for updating a product
Set the headers in format Authorization: Bearer token
http://localhost:4000/api/products/id

Delete request for updating a product
Set the headers in format Authorization: Bearer token
http://localhost:4000/api/products/id

Get request for getting all orders:
http://localhost:4000/api/orders

Post request for creating a product:
Set the headers in format Authorization: Bearer token
http://localhost:4000/api/orders

Patch request for updating the status of an order
Set the headers in format Authorization: Bearer token
{
  "status": "Processing"
}
http://localhost:4000/api/orders/id


